DTSTAMP:20260328T110752Z
DTSTART:20260411T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Westcrest Park.  \\nJoi
	n Dirt Corps this April to celebrate Earth Day month\\\, enjoy the flowers
	 and help us care for this section of the West Duwamish Greenbelt! We’ll b
	e learning about some of the early spring plants in this unique forest eco
	system in Westcrest Park. We’ll then be caring for our restoration area by
	 applying mulch around the native plants and trees and removing weeds (loo
	king at you blackberry!). We hope to see you there! \\nRegister\n\nhttps:/
